The '''Y60 Thalassian cargo hauler''' was a type of [[Freighter/Legends|freighter]] [[Starship/Legends|starship]]. The [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggler]] [[Pinchers]] owned one until it was "borrowed" by [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] in order to infiltrate the [[Cavrilhu Pirates|Cavrilhu Pirate]] [[Cavrilhu's Kauron base|base]] in the [[Kauron asteroid field]].

